    "description": {
      "zh": "9x18毫米PM PS gs PPO是一种执法部门使用的带有铅芯弹头的弹药，供内务部，FSSP和DOSAAF使用。",
      "en": "A 9x18mm Makarov PS gs PPO cartridge with a 6.3 gram lead core bullet with a bimetallic jacket in a truncated cone round-nose shape, in a steel case. The PS gs PPO cartridge was developed due to the need for the Ministry of Internal Affairs to equip law enforcement agencies with a cartridge that had reduced ricochet capabilities in order to minimize collateral damage during urban operations."
